dct_title_s: Map of the city of New York, 1850
dct_description_sm: Shows ward boundaries, parks, fire districts, and piers. Covers Manhattan south of 51st St. Oriented with north to the right. Inset: 12th Ward, city of New York. Includes fire alarm information and tables of correspondance between wards and other political divisions.
dct_publisher_sm: [New York : s.n., 1850] (N.Y. : [Lith. of G.] Hayward, 180 Fulton St.)
